Chino 'Fats' Williams https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chino_%27Fats%27_Williams 0 Chino 'Fats' Williams (July 26, 1933 – April 5, 2000) was an American actor.Williams was best known for such films and television series as The Terminator, Action Jackson, Road House, Rocky III, Weird Science, Iron Eagle, Storyville, House Party, and Baretta.
